msg: TUSCANY-1171 update readme for beta1 release, including new fixes and noting unimplemented SDO 2.1 features

author: jsdelfino
msg: Shutdown our WorkManager when the runtime gets stopped, to avoid leaking threads and the resources they hold, including open TCP/IP sockets. Changed the Jetty and Tomcat embedded servers to use our WorkScheduler. Changed the start order of the Tomcat engine, connector and registration of servlet mapping to fix connection refused and page not found exceptions.
